10:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"5. References"}]
11:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Check the references of your consultants. Your consultants should be able to provide you with recommendations. Read about the testimonials given by clients about your consultant before taking any decision. Client reference is a very effective means to choose the right ISO consultant to start your ISO certification process."}]
12:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"6. Results-Oriented"}]
13:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Make sure that the ISO consultant you prefer genuinely cares about the best results. Ask them the best ways to achieve the goals and work with them to create a new milestone for your business. Ask them for the case studies of their past projects to know how they have achieved the client’s goal."}]
